channel.title: Need a fully renamed 317 deob
channel.description:
Hey all, I was informed by a friend of mine, vbcoderx, that I could get a fully (or very close to) renamed deob for 317 on here.
I just want to see how the client handles a few things and see if I can rip a few of their algorithms for something I am working on.
I turned to the search button originally, but found nothing. Could be that I didn't use good search terms but I don't believe so.
Anyhow, if someone would be so kind as to link me to a post containing one, or upload it themselves and post the link.
Thanks a lot.

item.dc:creator: @Krichevskoy Krichevskoy
item.description:
@Krichevskoy wrote:

[quote=“Unhandled, post:12, topic:209350”][quote author=Pwnd link=topic=275743.msg2253750#msg2253750 date=1212289694]

You will struggle contacting wL.

I had sudden mental image of climbing a mountain in Tibet to reach the temple at the summit.
[/quote]Then walking in and finding the mighty wL with a bright aura around him?

With his fellow monks writing C code on stone tablets and worshipping the great GNU.[/quote]
It is rumored that their code, valid to certain arcane compilers, produces a dark program run only by the foolish and the foolhardy. But this is not why you have come.

examine throne
You see the legendary throne of winterlove. The label on the underside reads “Aeron”. A sign hangs haphazardly from the arms.

read sign
You first turn the sign level. Clearly, this place has seen some disuse.
It reads, “The guru is OUT.”
